## **Loop** `=>` Global Variables

```scss
html {
  @each $var, $color in $brand-colors {
    --#{$var}: #{$color};
  }
}
```

<!-- slide -->

## **Loop** `=>` Theme Variables

```scss
@each $name, $theme in $themes {
  [data-theme='#{$name}'] {
    @each $local, $global in $theme {
      --#{$local}: var(--#{$global});
    }
  }
}
```

